txt.en: Return the bandanas to Tagar in Jax Phanâl

'We cannot seem to rid ourselves of these vile goblins. I would like you to go to their encampment to the south-east of Jax Phanâl, collect their bandanas and return them to me as proof of their defeat.'
Collect goblin bandanas from Súlstrok or environs ([placeholder]/12)
'Excellent work, friend. It may take time, but I am certain that we will root out these goblins and make our lands safe, now that the Kindred are in charge.'
Tagar once again enlists you to collect trophies from the goblins south-east of Jax Phanâl.
Return the bandanas to Tagar in Jax Phanâl
'Will you go to their encampment and collect their bandanas? You will find it east and south of the outpost. Return to me when the effort is complete.'
'Do you remember my request? I would like you to go to the goblin encampment to the south-east of Jax Phanâl, collect their bandanas and return them to me as proof of their defeat.'

Tagar asked that you return to the goblins' encampment south and east of Jax Phanâl in a further attempt to remove the goblin threat from the area. You are to collect twelve of the goblins' bandanas, and return them to Tagar at his dwelling.
